
STEP-1 : Download, Install & Configure Docker on Linux :

# yum install docker -y

STEP-2 : Setup a Docker Group :

# groupadd docker

STEP-3 : Add user into Docker group :

# usermod -aG docker cloud_user 

STEP-4 : Enable & Start the Docker Deamon Service :

# systemctl enable docker 

# systemctl status docker 

# systemctl start docker 

# systemctl status docker 

STEP-5 : Logout from Admin user and cross check with Normal User:

# docker ps 

STEP-6 : Run our First Container 

# docker pull docker.io/hello-world

# docker images

# docker ps

# docker ps -a

# docker run hello-world

# docker ps -a 


Deploying a Static Website to the Container (Docker)

# docker run -d --name "FirstWebSite" -p 80:80 spacebones/doge

# docker images

# docker ps

